Demosaicing of an image by bilinear interpolation
--------------------------------------------------------------------
interpolation of pixels to retrieve image from CFA captured from CCD or CMOS digital camera.

Algorithm

Detailed steps of the algorithm can be found here:
http://www.peter-cockerell.net/Bayer/bayer.html


The resultant image has been demosaiced.